OL,6,FWarwickshire Fire and Rescue Service
OL,7,Fhas done a partial U-turn on removing
OL,8,Fon-call firefighters from the county's
OL,9,Fcrews.
OL,11,FInstead, new proposals will see the
OL,12,Fsystem remain in parts of the county,
OL,13,Fbut at night only.
