OL,3,CWarwickshire Fire Service does partial
OL,4,CU-turn on getting rid of on-call crews
OL,6,FThe Fire Service said at the beginning
OL,7,Fof the year that they needed to
OL,8,Frestructure the service to make sure
OL,9,Fthey are putting more crews where most
OL,10,Fincidents happen and because they say
OL,11,Fthey cannot recruit the number of on-
OL,12,Fcall fire crews that they need. On-
OL,13,Fcall crews work part-time alongside
OL,14,Fother jobs and can be at their local
OL,15,Fstation within five minutes when they
OL,16,Fare on call.
OL,18,FThe Fire Service has now responded to
OL,19,Fthe public consultation on the
OL,20,Fproposed plans and have amended them
OL,21,Ffollowing feedback.
