OL,3,CWarwickshire Fire Service does partial
OL,4,CU-turn on getting rid of on-call crews
OL,6,FIt means that instead of getting rid
OL,7,Fof on-call firefighters all over the
OL,8,Fcounty, the new proposal would see
OL,9,Fthem stay on at night only in
OL,10,FPolesworth, Henley-In-Arden,
OL,11,FWellesbourne, Southam and Bidford-On-
OL,12,FAvon.
OL,14,FFour fire stations which are currently
OL,15,Fon-call only stations will now get
OL,16,Ffull-time crews based there during the
OL,17,Fday. These are Kenilworth, Henley-In-
OL,18,FArden, Wellesbourne and Southam.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/7
