OL,3,CWarwickshire Fire Service does partial
OL,4,CU-turn on getting rid of on-call crews
OL,6,FOverall the number of fire crews
OL,7,Favailable would be 14 in the day and
OL,8,F13 at night. That is an improvement on
OL,9,Fthe current proposal of 12 in the day
OL,10,Fand eight at night, but a change from
OL,11,Fthe current system which has 11 in the
OL,12,Fday and nine at night, with the option
OL,13,Fof up to 12 more when on-call fire
OL,14,Fcrews are on duty.
OL,16,FThe amended proposals would also still
OL,17,Fsee response times lengthen in some
OL,18,Fparts of the county.
