OL,3,CWarwickshire Fire Service does partial
OL,4,CU-turn on getting rid of on-call crews
OL,6,FThe proposals will cost an extra #0.5
OL,7,Fmillion a year, with an additional
OL,8,F#600,000 needed to modify station
OL,9,Ffacilities. These finances are
OL,10,Fcurrently unbudgeted for.
OL,12,FThe Firefighter's Union the FRSA say
OL,13,Fthat for this reason 'These proposals
OL,14,Fwill result not only in a worse
OL,15,Fservice, but a more expensive one.'
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/7
