OL,3,CWarwickshire Fire Service does partial
OL,4,CU-turn on getting rid of on-call crews
OL,6,FThe Association President Mark Palmer
OL,7,Fsays the plans 'will make the on-call
OL,8,Fteams in seven stations redundant, the
OL,9,Fproposal will marginally improve
OL,10,Fresponse times in three districts and
OL,11,Fworsen it in the two districts with
OL,12,Fthe longest response times. All this
OL,13,Fwill cost council tax payers at least
OL,14,F#2.3 million over three years, which
OL,15,Fthey freely admit is unbudgeted and
OL,16,Fwill have to be taken from other
OL,17,Fservices.'
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G6/7
