OL,3,CWarwickshire Fire Service does partial
OL,4,CU-turn on getting rid of on-call crews
OL,6,F'The future is bleak for the on-call
OL,7,Fcrews at Stratford, Fenny Compton,
OL,8,FShipston, Kenilworth, Bedworth,
OL,9,FColeshill and Atherstone now facing
OL,10,Fredundancy. Shipston, Gaydon and Fenny
OL,11,FCompton stations will effectively
OL,12,Fclose for normal business.'
OL,14,FThe amended plans will now be
OL,15,Fdiscussed at the Resources and Fire
OL,16,Fand Rescue Overview and Scrutiny
OL,17,FCommittee meeting on Wednesday 26 June
OL,18,Fbefore going to Warwickshire County
OL,19,FCouncil's Cabinet meeting for a
OL,20,Fdecision on Tuesday 16 July.
